og/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n&quot;雖然成日都搵到我偷妳科技偷妳機密嘅證據,但其實一切都喺巧合,我仲未正式謀妳曬副身家,妳嘅制裁已經hurt到我,點睇都喺妳錯&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n&quot;仲有我想警告下妳,妳唔好以為制裁我就會驚,以為幫到我養啲妹仔同奴隸,妳制裁完我,我只會令佢過得更差,咁樣只會違背妳想佢有人權過得好嘅初衷,而且我相信就算我點強姦虐待佢,佢都會同我一條心&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n&quot;最後我想同我啲奴隸講下,唔會睇我老婆資本雄厚,科技強大又有飽飯食,而我治下咩都會爆炸又窮到要食草,其實如果真喺要離婚開戰,我打起上黎唔一定會輸&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n&quot;最後最後再警告你班奴隸,你嘅幸福由我主宰,以為推翻我就有好日子過?其實喺下下策&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n啲邏輯仲差過我中一作文<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e316f9d2d9c7c29122464acfc1577e67c1301461","tid":2174573,"uid":135762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2fed2a3318e55de83d91aab771667da94e4dc100","tid":2174573,"uid":174060,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T03:55:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Pi9DWta.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPi9DWta.gif&h=97d6e78e&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T04:57:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d270dc2d82d260fec4fd4b711e2aae66f711e59","tid":2174573,"uid":195084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited